<p class="">May I ask the hon. and gallant Member whether he has read the cicular Note issued by the British Government to other members of the League inquiring whether, if Italy took military action against us arising out of sanctions, they would give us military help under the Covenant of the League, and has he read the answer that all the Mediterranean Powers were unanimous to <span id="78" class="column-number" data-column-number="78"></span> the effect that they would fulfil their obligations?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
