<p class="">Was it not the British Government which first moved to take off sanctions?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-c2f49be7-8a59-4e31-8b07-245f40c892b8" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
